gatling testing code

Usage

Export Examples:
  java GatlingCodeArchiver.java export
  java GatlingCodeArchiver.java export /path/to/project
  java GatlingCodeArchiver.java export /path/to/project /path/to/output.html

Import Examples:
  java GatlingCodeArchiver.java import input.html
  java GatlingCodeArchiver.java import input.html /path/to/restored/dir

Defaults:
  Export: current directory -> gatling.code.html
  Import: -> ./import directory
